---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Physical Site Review | Sheepdog Cyber Defense" description="Physical security assessment for Texas businesses. Evaluate physical security controls, access controls, and facility vulnerabilities." showMatrix={true}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Service",
    "name": "Physical Site Review",
    "description": "Assessment of physical security including building access controls, perimeter security, video surveillance, and visitor management.",
    "provider": {
      "@type": "LocalBusiness",
      "name": "Sheepdog Cyber Defense",
      "url": "https://sheepdogcyberdefense.com"
    },
    "areaServed": {
      "@type": "State",
      "name": "Texas"
    },
    "serviceType": "Physical Security Assessment",
    "url": "https://sheepdogcyberdefense.com/services/physical-site-review"
  }
  </script>
  <section>
    <h1>Physical Site Review</h1>
    <p class="lead">We assess the physical security of your facilities to identify vulnerabilities that could allow unauthorized access.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What It Covers</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Building access controls</li>
      <li>Perimeter security</li>
      <li>Video surveillance systems</li>
      <li>Locking mechanisms and entry points</li>
      <li>Visitor management procedures</li>
      <li>Security lighting</li>
      <li>Environmental security</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p>We conduct a hands-on assessment of your physical premises, looking for weaknesses that could be exploited by an attacker. This includes observing physical controls, testing access points, and reviewing security policies.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Deliverables</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Findings report with photos</li>
      <li>Risk-rated vulnerabilities</li>
      <li>Physical security recommendations</li>
      <li>Executive summary</li>
      <li>Debrief call</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Typical Timeline</h2>
    <p>Most physical site reviews complete within 1-2 days on-site, depending on the number of locations and complexity.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What You'll Need</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Site access authorization</li>
      <li>Floor plans (if available)</li>
      <li>Existing security policies</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <a href="/contact" class="btn">Request a Quote</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead { font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 700px; }
  section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .cta { padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
</style>
